PC Number: 2023-0682

Date: 2023-06-23

Whereas The Watson Lake and District Chamber of Commerce, in Yukon, the certificate of formation of which was recorded under the Boards of Trade Act on November 18, 1963, has ceased to exercise its franchises;

 

Therefore, Her Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Industry, dissolves The Watson Lake and District Chamber of Commerce under section 43 of the Boards of Trade Act.


Attendu que The Watson Lake and District Chamber of Commerce (Yukon), dont le certificat de formation a été enregistré en vertu de la Loi sur les chambres de commerce le 18 novembre 1963, a cessé d’exercer ses pouvoirs,

 

À ces causes, sur recommandation du ministre de l’Industrie et en vertu de l’article 43 de la Loi sur les chambres de commerce, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil dissout The Watson Lake and District Chamber of Commerce.
